data.comment:
Mapping the Taiga CSV reports with the columns that are already in the CLI:

 

Title -> subject

Description -> description

State -> status

Business Value -> No column present, but we can assign a
random value that’s already present in the biscuit

Initiated Date -> created_date

Planned Date -> No column present and we can set Not Yet
Set

Due Date -> due_date

Tasks # -> tasks

Points -> total-points
